        Samplitude Pro X2 Suite combines the outstanding features of  
        Samplitude Pro X2 audio workstation with a first-class add-on 
        package.                                                      
                                                                    
  Football Manager Real Time Editor (FMRTE) is a 3rd party real time editor   
  for Football Manager, and it's available since 2008. With FMRTE you can     
  scout players, find good deals, and of course, edit almost every thing      
  the game has.                                                               
                                                                              
  Did you ever wanted to give your team some extra points?                    
  With FMRTE you can edit competitions standings, colours, and reputation.    
                                                                              
  Almost everything can be edited in a player. Hair/skin colour, his          
  attributes, his relationships, clubs registration, contracts. For clubs     
  you can edit finances (this include, loans, debts...), kits colours,        
  stadium, attendance, teams reputation, relationships, and so on.            
                                                                              
  FMRTE includes a powerful and fast search filter, that allows you to        
  personalize your search. Making it easy for you to find what you want       
  when you want.                                                              
                                                                              
  FMRTE gives you the control over players transfers. You can edit all        
  future transfer details like: transfer date, amount, player to be           
  transfered, destination.
